freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: On the 3rd day after the 2nd vaccine dose,  I woke up dizzy with a headache and abdominal discomfort. After taking tylenol the headache and eventually abdominal discomfort went away. The dizziness slowly tapered away and today I feel great.
